title: Photos: Santa Maria Elks Rodeo parade
content: Santa Maria Valley's 75th annual "Denim and Diamonds" Elks Rodeo Parade featured community members, dignitaries, student marching bands, horses and floats.   Close   1 of 72   Banda Tierra Nueva plays "Deep in the Heart of Texas" with the El Arenal group Saturday during the Elks Rodeo Parade on Broadway.   Len Wood, Staff   Blake Fumia, 3, and Ava Renteria, 2, blow bubbles Saturday during the Elks Rodeo Parade on Broadway.   Len Wood, Staff   Marchers from the Marine Corp League Coastal Valley Detachment 1340 wave flags during the Elks Rodeo Parade, Saturday on Broadway.   Len Wood Staff   Performers from the Hancock College Youth Ballet Folklorico dance Saturday during the Elks Rodeo Parade on Broadway.   Len Wood, Staff   A vaquero from Rancho de Nipomo rides a bull during the Elks Rodeo Parade, Saturday on Broadway.   Len Wood Staff   Star of the Parade Pryor Baird, who performed on "The Voice," waves from a truck during the Elks Rodeo Parade on Saturday on Broadway.
